{"tid":874662,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"美智庫指中國加入世貿導致美國累計流失340萬個職位 74%為製造業","createTime":"2018-10-24T10:59:44.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-25T23:10:18.000Z","uid":141151,"like":13,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"b632e7fa112c24e091ffcf0a4f68fa581c53d021","tid":874662,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-24T10:59:44.000Z","msg":"美智庫指中國加入世貿導致美國累計流失340萬個職位 74%為製造業<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.aastocks.com/tc/stocks/news/aafn-news/NOW.903423/2\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.aastocks.com%2Ftc%2Fstocks%2Fnews%2Faafn-news%2FNOW.903423%2F2&d=oV03Jz3tVDaVEDGqvmAcKDA5unq%2FSd9ZKvr75NUD1%2F0%3D&h=af7dcc5a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.aastocks.com/tc/stocks/news/aafn-news/NOW.903423/2</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n《華爾街日報》報道，美國智庫經濟政策研究所(Economic Policy Institute)發表報告指，中國自2001年加入世界貿易組織(WTO)後，美國貿易逆差出現爆發式增長，估計導致美國在2001年至2017年流失340萬個職位，其中製造業佔74%。報告指，失去製造業工作的工人往往退出勞動市場，美國國內需求減少亦導致職位流失覆蓋全美國各地。按行業計，以電腦及電子零部件業貿易逆差增長最快，導致120萬個職位流失。"},{"pid":"919c3fb54e6e3c9d9d8f8416247299c53ceb854c","tid":874662,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-24T11:18:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a9a48651f1c63239ff396750ef474973fdb652bc","tid":874662,"uid":31071,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-24T12:10:08.000Z","msg":"中國或許成為最大贏家<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a2e5c0b5c99d2b6f324164cd59f5523d03e3fab4","tid":874662,"uid":121146,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-24T12:26:37.000Z","msg":"奧巴馬又種左棵大樹<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"529f3e594f4702388208f8d6a76b32445abbd06a","tid":874662,"uid":132859,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-24T12:37:40.000Z","msg":"強姦犯克林頓做嘅好事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7d7e30e94d75